premise_source_doc_sentence: Caryn Mandabach produced ground-breaking US hits including The Cosby Show , Roseanne , A Different World  (  1990 -- 1993  )  , Grace Under Fire  (  1993 -- 1998  )  , Cybill  (  1995 -- 1998  )  , 3rd Rock from the Sun  (  1997 -- 2001  )  , That '80s Show  (  2002  )  , That '70s Show  (  1998 -- 2004  )  , and Grounded for Life  (  2001 -- 2005  )  .
In with the Flynns is a British sitcom created by Caryn Mandabach , produced by Caryn Mandabach Productions , and broadcast by the BBC .

The sitcom was produced by Carsey-Werner Productions and YBYL Productions , with Shepherd , Lorre , Howard Gould , Jay Daniel , Caryn Mandabach , Marcy Carsey , and Tom Werner serving as the show 's original executive producers .
